Description:
        NOTE: You must use the GHC head branch > 6.13.20100309 to get decent performance.
        Implementation of Buchberger's algorithm using the Repa array library.

Synopsis:
        Implementation of Buchberger's algorithms using the Repa array library.

Tested-with: GHC == 6.13.20100309, GHC == 6.12.1

Library
  Build-Depends: 
        base                 == 4.*,
        dph-base             == 0.4.*,
        repa                 == 1.1.*,
        HaskellForMaths      == 0.1.*,
        dph-prim-seq         == 0.4.*,
        containers           == 0.3.*,
        dph-par              == 0.4.*

  ghc-options:
        -Odph -Wall -fno-warn-missing-signatures -fglasgow-exts

  extensions:
        UndecidableInstances
        PArr

  Exposed-modules:
        Yaiba.Monomial
        Yaiba.Polynomial
        Yaiba.Ideal
